mu8QEolm1mb9IWDAoKoC4zIM7kL04i2SvfEt96HbeOXZQ ). What couldn=E2=80=99t be c=
hanged was nature: IBM was a company predicated on breadth, not specializat=
ion; that=E2=80=99s why Gerstner was right to not break apart the company b=
ut to instead deliver Internet solutions to enterprises. Similarly, Microso=
ft was a company predicated on integration around Windows; the company=E2=
